        <title>Parallel Media Encoder</title>
        <item>
            <title>Version 1.03</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
<h3>What's New in 1.03</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Fixed:</b> Blackmagic RAW runtime is now embedded in the app — BRAW files no longer require a separate Blackmagic RAW SDK or Player install</li>
  <li><b>Fixed:</b> RED R3D decoding now falls back to OpenCL or CPU when Metal GPU is unavailable (e.g. virtual machines)</li>
  <li><b>Fixed:</b> Improved error messages when RAW codec initialization fails</li>
  <li><b>Fixed:</b> Settings window and console now render correctly on Light Mode systems</li>
  <li><b>New:</b> Welcome screen on first launch lets you enter a license key right away</li>
</ul>
            ]]></description>
