        <item>
            <title>Version 1.02</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
<h3>What's New in 1.02</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Fixed:</b> MXF frame rate conversion no longer stalls on longer files (e.g. 24fps → 30fps)</li>
  <li><b>Fixed:</b> Frame rate upconversion now correctly duplicates frames to maintain duration</li>
  <li><b>Fixed:</b> DNx media color accuracy — output now matches source contrast and includes correct BT.709 color tags</li>
  <li><b>New:</b> Quit confirmation when encodes are running — no more accidental data loss</li>
  <li><b>New:</b> Dock icon progress bar shows encode progress while the app is in the background</li>
  <li><b>New:</b> Low frame rate options (5, 10, 15 fps) added to encoding settings</li>
</ul>
            ]]></description>
